getFirstRawFieldDataFromManyFields

public String getFirstRawFieldDataFromManyFields(String... tags)
Get the first found field value from an array of fields. e.g. if you search a title you can supply "TI", "J2", "T1", "T2" and "T3" to get the first one in that order with a value.

Parameters:
tags - seperated list or array of tags
Returns:
field value if any was found or null
